            <div class="no-sale-guarantee">
              <h3>üö´ We Never Sell Your Data</h3>
              <p>
                We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes. 
                Your data is not a revenue stream for us.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="sharing-scenarios">
              <h3>When We Might Share Information:</h3>
              
              <div class="scenario">
                <h4>Service Providers</h4>
                <p>
                  We share limited data with trusted service providers who help us operate our website:
                </p>
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>Email Service:</strong> To send newsletters (data processing agreement in place)</li>
                  <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics (anonymized data only)</li>
                  <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Netlify (for website hosting and performance)</li>
                  <li><strong>AI Services:</strong> Anthropic/OpenAI (for content analysis - no personal data)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="scenario">
                <h4>Legal Requirements</h4>
                <p>
                  We may disclose information if required by law, such as:
                </p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Court orders or legal subpoenas</li>
                  <li>Government investigations</li>
                  <li>Protecting our legal rights</li>
                  <li>Preventing fraud or illegal activity</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="scenario">
                <h4>Business Transfers</h4>
                <p>
                  If GlowPicked is acquired or merged, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction. 
                  You'll be notified of any such change.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cookies-tracking">
